::Skulletron::

	Skulletron looked at Feline as she patted the seat next to her and smiled
at him.  Skulletron quickly smiled at Feline and then looked at Zardus,
making sure not to be seen.  Then he crept over into the chair beside
Feline.  He leaned over and whispered, "You know, you don't seem half as
bad as I thought you'd be."
